name: Pandora-to-Spotify
tagline: Grab thumbed-up tracks from Pandora and make Spotify playlist
body:
# Pandora to Spotify Playlist Converter
 
A Google Chrome extension that grabs thumbed-up tracks on your Pandora stations and converts into Spotify playlist.

**[Download](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/cgkmfkggcmoclhipfkabaemflflellek)**
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
